Package org.dockbox.selene.core.events.server

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ServerEvent
    The abstract type which can be used to listen to all server related events.
    ServerEvent.ServerInitEvent
    The event fired when the server is initiating/initializing.
    ServerEvent.ServerPostInitEvent
    The event fired when the server is done initiating/initializing.
    ServerEvent.ServerReloadEvent
    The event fired when a server-wide reload is performed.
    ServerEvent.ServerStartedEvent
    The event fired when the server is done starting.
    ServerEvent.ServerStartingEvent
    The event fired when the server is starting.
    ServerEvent.ServerStoppingEvent
    The event fired when the server is stopping.
